ght: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Identify high-converting, commercial-intent keywords in your niche<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uncover low-competition opportunities your competitors may be ignoring<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Group keywords into themed ad groups based on buyer intent (e.g. awareness, comparison, purchase)<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choose the right match types and negative keywords to minimise waste<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Outline the messaging and offers that will resonate best with your audience<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This stage is where your competitive edge is built in strategy, not spend.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Campaign Build-Out and Ad Copywriting<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We structure your campaigns and write compelling, high-performance ad copy based on our research:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ad groups are created around tightly themed keyword sets<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ads are written with strong CTAs, emotional drivers, and benefit-led language<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All available ad extensions (cal