ow what to expect and what it takes to succeed. Below are the most common questions Kenyan businesses ask us before launching their first campaign.<\/div><\/div>[vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How much budget should I start with?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052221-d2dccac3-2f8e82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"526\">There\u2019s no one-size-fits-all answer, but we generally recommend starting with a <strong data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"475\">minimum of KES 20,000\u201330,000 per month<\/strong> for small to mid-sized campaigns. This allows for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"670\">\n<li data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"567\">\n<p data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"567\">Enough data to optimise effectively<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"568\" data-end=\"621\">\n<p data-start=\"570\" data-end=\"621\">Testing multiple keyword groups and ad variations<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"670\">\n<p data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"670\">Sufficient reach without blowing your budget<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"915\">Higher budgets are often needed for industries like legal, finance, or e-commerce where <strong data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"786\">click costs are higher<\/strong> due to competition. That said, we always align your budget to your business goals \u2014 and maximise every shilling with zero waste.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can I run Google Ads myself without an agency?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1078\">Yes, but here\u2019s the reality: Google\u2019s default settings are designed to spend your money fast, not wisely.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1127\">Without professional guidance, most businesses:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1128\" data-end=\"1274\">\n<li data-start=\"1128\" data-end=\"1157\">\n<p data-start=\"1130\" data-end=\"1157\">Target the wrong keywords<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1158\" data-end=\"1194\">\n<p data-start=\"1160\" data-end=\"1194\">Write generic or low-CTR ad copy<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1195\" data-end=\"1225\">\n<p data-start=\"1197\" data-end=\"1225\">Overlook negative keywords<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1274\">\n<p data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1274\">Fail to set up conversion tracking correctly<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1506\">This leads to high costs, poor leads, and frustration. Working with a certified agency like Aminifu Digital means your campaign is <strong data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1448\">structured for profitability from day one <\/strong>and\u00a0constantly optimised to outperform your competition.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How quickly will I see results?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1549\" data-end=\"1767\">Google Ads can start delivering clicks within <strong data-start=\"1595\" data-end=\"1617\">hours of launching<\/strong>. However, we typically advise a <strong data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1698\">testing and optimisation period of 2\u20134 weeks<\/strong> to gather data, refine targeting, and identify winning combinations.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1793\">Here\u2019s a basic timeline:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1794\" data-end=\"1989\">\n<li data-start=\"1794\" data-end=\"1841\">\n<p data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1841\">Week 1: Campaign live, early data collected<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1842\" data-end=\"1880\">\n<p data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1880\">Week 2: First round of adjustments<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"1939\">\n<p data-start=\"1883\" data-end=\"1939\">Weeks 3\u20134: Optimisations kick in, performance improves<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1940\" data-end=\"1989\">\n<p data-start=\"1942\" data-end=\"1989\">Month 2+: Scaling and efficiency improvements<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1991\" data-end=\"2075\">Results can be even faster if you already have strong offers and good landing pages.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What\u2019s the difference between Google Search and Display Ads?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2147\" data-end=\"2294\"><strong data-start=\"2147\" data-end=\"2168\">Google Search Ads<\/strong> show up when someone <em data-start=\"2190\" data-end=\"2209\">actively searches<\/em> for a keyword \u2014 for example, \u201cbest accountant Nairobi\u201d or \u201cbuy running shoes Kenya.\u201d<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2296\" data-end=\"2459\"><strong data-start=\"2296\" data-end=\"2318\">Google Display Ads<\/strong> show up on websites, apps, and YouTube \u2014 based on user behaviour or interests, even when they\u2019re <em data-start=\"2416\" data-end=\"2431\">not searching<\/em>. These are more suited for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2461\" data-end=\"2522\">\n<li data-start=\"2461\" data-end=\"2480\">\n<p data-start=\"2463\" data-end=\"2480\">Brand awareness<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2481\" data-end=\"2496\">\n<p data-start=\"2483\" data-end=\"2496\">Remarketing<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2497\" data-end=\"2522\">\n<p data-start=\"2499\" data-end=\"2522\">Top-of-funnel traffic<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2678\">We recommend starting with <strong data-start=\"2551\" data-end=\"2565\">Search Ads<\/strong> if your priority is <strong data-start=\"2586\" data-end=\"2621\">lead generation or direct sales<\/strong> \u2014 they target people already looking for what you offer.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Do you also handle remarketing campaigns?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2731\" data-end=\"2952\">Yes. In fact, <strong data-start=\"2745\" data-end=\"2778\">remarketing is a crucial part<\/strong> of your overall Google Ads strategy. Many users don\u2019t convert on the first visit, but with remarketing, you can re-engage them across the Google Display Network or YouTube.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"2964\">We set up:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2965\" data-end=\"3133\">\n<li data-start=\"2965\" data-end=\"3003\">\n<p data-start=\"2967\" data-end=\"3003\">Dynamic remarketing for e-commerce<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3004\" data-end=\"3032\">\n<p data-start=\"3006\" data-end=\"3032\">Custom audience segments<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3033\" data-end=\"3088\">\n<p data-start=\"3035\" data-end=\"3088\">Visual retargeting ads with promotions or reminders<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3089\" data-end=\"3133\">\n<p data-start=\"3091\" data-end=\"3133\">Cross-device and cross-platform tracking<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3135\" data-end=\"3228\">It\u2019s one of the most cost-effective ways to increase conversions without increasing ad spend.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_single_image image=&#8221;5595&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; lazy_loading=&#8221;true&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;] Why Google Search Ads Are a Powerful Growth Channel Google Search Ads have become one of the most effective digital m